 data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xqk1767361099123.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xqk1767361099123.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xqk1767361099123.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xqk1767361099123\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the following steps to configure the Layout Mode property in the IDE.</p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"xqk1767361099123__step_w1667ab1b5b1b1_w1668ab1b5b1_w1669ab1b5_w1670ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Open your DSP in the Component Editor.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"xqk1767361099123__step_w1671ab1b5b1b3_w1672ab1b5b1_w1673ab1b5_w1674ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Select the component (not individual fields or entities).</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"xqk1767361099123__step_w1675ab1b5b1b5_w1676ab1b5b1_w1677ab1b5_w1678ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the Property Inspector, locate the <strong class=\"ph b\">Layout Mode</strong> property.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"xqk1767361099123__step_w1679ab1b5b1b7_w1680ab1b5b1_w1681ab1b5_w1682ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Select the appropriate value from the dropdown.</span>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"example\" id=\"xqk1767361099123__example_cx4_yjj_vhc\">\n<p class=\"p\">All DSPs default to Full Document mode (D) to ensure compatibility. The Layout Mode\n\t\t\t\tproperty can be changed as needed for your development approach.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_27055514\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_27055514\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Setting the Layout Mode Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 02, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Use the following steps to configure the Layout Mode property in the IDE. Open your DSP in the Component Editor. Select the component (not individual fields or entities). In the Property Inspector, locate the Layout Mode property. Select the appropriate value from the dropdown. All DSPs default to Full Document mode (D) to ensure compatibility. The Layout Mode property can be changed as needed for your development approach. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}